fun with construction paper creations cut-paper play is an excellent collection of over 80 kid-approved construction paper creations for children ages 4 to 10 . the projects are grouped by 3 different skill and difficulty levels . a variety of techniques is shown . all you need is different kinds of paper or cardboard , scissors , glue , sometimes yarn or a stapler . so the crafts are inexpensive , but very amazing . two- and three-dimensional projects , mobiles and seasonal projects are shown . we got inspiration for many more paper projects for the future